videos.description: Jeff Green receives the slick pass from Kyrie Irving and takes flight to dunk on Aaron Nesmith under the basket.

videos.description: Kevin Durant easily blows by Aaron Nesmith and rises up to flush down a powerful one-handed slam dunk.

videos.description: To finish out the preseason, Kevin Durant scores 25 points and racks up three blocks in 27 minutes of play as the Nets go on to blow out the Celtics 113-89.
